# supported

**Type Property**

A Boolean value that indicates the newly created passkey supports the PRF extension.

## Declaration

```swift
static var supported: ASAuthorizationPublicKeyCredentialPRFRegistrationOutput { get }
```

## Using defined support values

- **unsupported**: A Boolean value that indicates the newly created passkey doesn’t support the PRF extension.
